      "content": "# Workspace Detection Plan\n\n- [x] Load mandatory common AI-DLC rules and welcome message.\n- [x] Resolve the active AI-DLC rule details directory.\n- [x] Scan extension opt-in prompts without loading full optional rule files.\n- [x] Inspect the existing AI-DLC state and audit trail.\n- [x] Scan the workspace to classify the project and identify the stack.\n- [x] Check for reverse-engineering artifacts and determine the next phase.\n- [x] Update workflow tracking files for this request.\n"
